snippet.title: Kaiserpunk - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Overseer Games invites you to build a city to rule the world in Kaiserpunk, a grand city builder blending production-focused city building with the world conquest of strategy games in an alternate 20th century world. Manage your city, grow industries, build a military, and defeat rivals to become the greatest empire.

--
Buy now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2012190/KAISERPUNK/
